l oscillations) and scale-free (neuronal avalanches)\ndynamics in brain activity occurs close to a non-equilibrium critical point at\nthe onset of self-sustained oscillations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Aug 2021 08:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 14:30:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
