he gas transport characteristics for the Knudsen number in the range of 0.05\nto 20.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Aug 2021 08:26:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 10:13:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-03"}
